OL,3,CMystery after river turns milky blue
OL,5,FThe River Ogmore, near Newbridge
OL,6,FFields in Bridgend, has turned a
OL,7,Fstriking milky blue colour, according
OL,8,Fto people in the area.
OL,10,FPictures sent to ITV News this morning
OL,11,F(6th March) appeared to show that the
OL,12,Friver had changed colour, raising
OL,13,Fconcerns about a suspected pollution
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FOne resident described the situation,
OL,17,Fand said, "it looks very bad."
