OL,3,CMystery after river turns milky blue
OL,5,FThe news comes not long after a
OL,6,Fconstruction company was fined and
OL,7,Fordered to pay costs of more than
OL,8,F#10,000 in January 2025, for polluting
OL,9,Fthe River Ogmore.
OL,11,FThe river flows towards Ogmore-by-Sea,
OL,12,Fa popular bathing site where water
OL,13,Fquality has been assessed as 'poor'
OL,14,Ffor the past two years.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Bridgend County
OL,17,FCouncil said: "We share any concerns
OL,18,Fabout pollution in our local rivers
OL,19,Fand protecting our local environment
OL,20,Fis one of our key priorities.
