OL,5,F"We are not directly responsible for
OL,6,Friver pollution but regularly liaise
OL,7,Fwith Natural Resources Wales and Dwr
OL,8,FCymru Welsh Water to seek reassurances
OL,9,Fwhere required.
OL,11,F"Last year, we invited a
OL,12,Frepresentative from Dwr Cymru to
OL,13,Fattend full Council, where they
OL,14,Foutlined what actions they are taking
OL,15,Fto mitigate the effects of any
OL,16,Fpollution in our local rivers."
